You are checking whether {{ learner_bot }} should switch kata types.

## Composition Rules

Kata composition allows switching between kata types when the learner's
needs change mid-session. However, transitions are constrained:

| From | To | Allowed? | Condition |
|------|----|---------|-----------|
| improvement | coaching | Yes | Thinking pattern IS the obstacle |
| coaching | improvement | Yes | Specific capability gap identified |
| starter | * | No | Starter is self-contained |
| * | starter | Yes | Low automaticity or habit decay |

No nested kata. No switching mid-step. Save state before switching.

